Feature: Can CRUD accounts
  In order manipulate my accounts
  As a user
  I can create,read, update my accounts but not delete


  Scenario: Create account
    Given I am logged in
    When I am in New account page
    And Account number is present
    Then I can create a new account

  Scenario: Read account
    Given I am in index page
    And I go to show account 
    Then I can view an existing account

  Scenario: Update account
    Given I am logged in
    When I am in All accounts page
    And I go to show account 
    Then I can view an existing account 
 
  Scenario: Delete account
    Given I am logged in
    When I am in All accounts page
    Then there is no destroy button
